{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Dread Flats&quot;</strong> is a first-person realistic horror game with a combination of unknown entity themes and Chinese elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will experience an intense sense of claustrophobia and horror, carefully designed scary points, a 1990s Chinese atmosphere, and mysterious, eerie, and twisted unknown entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Plot Synopsis </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A paranormal live streamer went missing during a night visit to the infamous &quot;Fangjiang Apartment&quot; and some eerie footage has been circulating on the internet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In order to prevent any more outsiders from entering, Fangjiang Apartment began hiring security guards to patrol the premises, but none of the guards lasted very long. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some say there really are ghosts in the apartment, while others say there is only one resident, Room 403. And you, are the newly hired security guard for Fangjiang Apartment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7Exploring with Light Interaction </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game will focus on exploration and interactive play, where players can interact with many objects in the environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7Check the surveillance cameras. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A light monitoring gameplay, where players can view surveillance cameras from the security room to ensure their own safety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stealth and countermeasures </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game will provide players with strategies to combat the imposters and ensure their survival. You can choose to sneak and hide, or find other ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00b7Pursuit </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A meticulously crafted chase sequence, an unforgettable chase experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/02gif.gif?t=1733886394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/1727590781469.gif?t=1733886394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/extras/03gif.gif?t=1733886394\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733886394","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733886394","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/637bdeb628a4e363ea04d0d3a6f88e477edb0817/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733886394","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114900/637bdeb628a4e363ea04d0d3a6f88e477edb0817/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733886394","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Dark day, simple scare"},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Dread Flats&quot;</strong> is a first-person realistic horror game with a combination of unknown entity themes and Chinese elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will experience an intense sense of claustrophobia and horror, carefully designed scary points, a 1990s Chinese atmosphere, and mysterious, eerie, and twisted unknown entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </